Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.03,0:00:07.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat, cepat!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.00,0:00:07.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siap!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.16,0:00:12.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat, nanti ada yang mendahului kita!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.55,0:00:13.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siap!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.86,0:00:17.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Upah kali ini jumlahnya lumayan besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.00,0:00:18.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semangat...!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.66,0:00:27.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.09,0:00:29.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bunuh mereka!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.37,0:00:34.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya kita bisa mengamuk sampai puas.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.40,0:00:37.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sulit dipercaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.90,0:00:41.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rupanya mereka mengambil\Nmetode kasar seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.75,0:00:47.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak, sebaiknya kita kabur\Nmelalui jalur bawah tanah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.30,0:00:51.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, lebih baik kita manfaatkan\Nkekacauan ini untuk kabur ke luar kota.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah mengirim\Nseluruh penyerang kita, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.66,0:00:56.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.86,0:01:00.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shiji Bau mengabari bahwa\Ndia merekrut "Paus Logam".
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.83,0:01:02.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paus Logam, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.33,0:01:06.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak yakin mereka akan tiba tepat waktu.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.23,0:01:09.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kirim petualang yang masih bisa bergerak\Nuntuk mengurus para penyusup itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.60,0:01:12.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo Forbartz.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.95,0:01:16.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau sudah seperti ini, kita perlu\Nmembunuh penjalin kontrak dengan "Dewi".
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.20,0:01:20.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iri, tolong jangan jauh-jauh dariku.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.43,0:01:22.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik, Kak.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.36,0:01:24.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan melindungimu\Nmeski nyawa taruhannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.86,0:01:26.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.23,0:01:29.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keluarga saling berkorban nyawa\Nuntuk satu sama lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.23,0:01:33.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itulah wujud keluarga yang hakiki.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.11,0:03:11.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo sialan itu.\NKuharap semua ini bagian dari rencananya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.29,0:03:14.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semoga saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau benar,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.20,0:03:18.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,rencananya benar-benar asal!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.17,0:03:22.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maju, habisi mereka!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada-ada saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.70,0:03:33.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, siapa selanjutnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.63,0:03:36.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau lumayan juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga, yang benar saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.44,0:03:41.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku baru saja berjualan, tahu.\NNanti rusak, dong!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.56,0:03:47.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.70,0:03:53.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Tidak mungkin...\N- Tokoku...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.56,0:04:11.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, cobalah menahan diri sedikit!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.03,0:04:13.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini untuk menutup jalur bala bantuan!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.61,0:04:18.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak kecil!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.79,0:04:21.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.13,0:04:24.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada berapa banyak?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.57,0:04:25.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.91,0:04:31.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak perlu takut pada anak-anak\Nselama waspada pada serangan dari bawah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.20,0:04:33.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu itu, tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.21,0:04:34.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lambat!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Segel kilat lembayung, "Gwemel", ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah paham cara melawan mereka?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.40,0:04:48.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Kesatria Suci.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.23,0:04:50.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo, apa rencana kita setelah ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.60,0:04:55.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuharap isi kepalamu masih\Nlebih baik dari buah-buahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita perbesar keributannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan begitu,\NLideo Sodrik takkan diam saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.50,0:05:06.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rupanya isi kepalamu jauh\Nlebih buruk dari buah-buahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa-bisanya rencana seperti...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.56,0:05:09.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cukup sampai di sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.08,0:05:18.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian yang sudah merusak\Nkedamaian kota, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Persiapkan diri kalian!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.71,0:05:24.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa mereka?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.70,0:05:27.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa mereka yang dipercaya\Nmenjaga keamanan kota ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kelihatannya begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.13,0:05:32.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya kalian tak mengenal kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.52,0:05:36.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami adalah petualang\Nterbaik dari Kota Ioff!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.00,0:05:40.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamilah yang berlari dari balik\Npercikan darah, Brigade "Pemburu Raksasa"!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak kenal.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.86,0:05:45.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya, jangan beri ampun!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.79,0:05:46.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tongkat petir!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.48,0:05:49.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tembak!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar bodoh! Kau membidik ke mana?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.95,0:05:55.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sungguh lelucon yang memuakkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.34,0:06:00.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tembak, tembak, tembak!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.76,0:06:03.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau ada yang kena,\Nkita dapat banyak untung!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daya serang dan akurasinya\Nbenar-benar rendah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.20,0:06:08.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rupanya hanya alat\Nuntuk memeriahkan festival.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.16,0:06:12.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian urus yang di sini!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.47,0:06:15.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu. Jangan serahkan\Norang-orang tak jelas ini pada kami!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.34,0:06:52.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa pun yang melukai aku dan Xylo berarti\Nmenyatakan perang pada keluarga Mastibolt.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.83,0:06:54.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sesali perbuatan kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.31,0:06:56.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kalian memang\Nmemikirkan kebaikan kota,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.46,0:06:59.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,berhenti lakukan hal seperti ini\Ndan bekerja yang giat!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.55,0:07:02.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rupanya kalian bisa akrab juga, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.84,0:07:11.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Troll?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.86,0:07:14.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa Sodrick juga memelihara seekor faerie?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.54,0:07:19.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,itu bukan sekadar hewan peliharaan\Nyang nakal, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.47,0:07:39.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita lebih unggul sekarang!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.26,0:07:41.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, pojokan mereka!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siap!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.05,0:07:43.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maju!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.59,0:07:46.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau itu memang niat kalian...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.09,0:07:49.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.61,0:07:50.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ehem!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.76,0:07:54.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kuduga,\Nengkau pasti membutuhkan mukjizatku!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.57,0:08:00.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kesatriaku, situasi ini adalah hukuman\Nkarena engkau pergi meninggalkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.54,0:08:05.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan tetapi, aku,\NDewi yang maha pengasih akan menolongmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.58,0:08:08.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, semuanya. Mari kita mulai!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.33,0:08:10.24,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Ayo, ayo!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.87,0:08:12.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus minta maaf\Npada Siena dan Zofflec nanti.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.43,0:08:13.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa mereka?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.52,0:08:16.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anggap ini saran dariku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.40,0:08:19.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebaiknya kalian semua kabur,\Natau menyerah saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau tidak, kalian akan mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak, lewat sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.71,0:08:33.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita tak perlu terpancing provokasi mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.12,0:08:36.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang terpenting adalah mereka\Ntak mengetahui lokasi kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.62,0:08:41.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akulah raja Federasi\NKerajaan Zef-Zelay Meth Kioh,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.26,0:08:43.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Norgalle Sendrige Pertama!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.63,0:08:45.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Wahai rakyatku yang...\N- Berisik!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Siapa kau?!\N- Cari mati, ya?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.25,0:08:48.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Turun, sini!\N- Pergi, sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.86,0:08:49.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mati, sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.61,0:08:52.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sungguh disayangkan,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.90,0:08:56.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku terpaksa memberikan hukuman\Ndi luar proses pengadilan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.83,0:09:03.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menjatuhkan hukuman eksekusi mati\Nkarena ledakan atas pemberontakan kalian!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.84,0:09:11.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial. Habisi dia!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.43,0:09:29.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maju!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.92,0:09:35.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada kavaleri, ya?\NMerepotkan sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.63,0:09:38.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.99,0:09:42.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.74,0:09:43.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.71,0:09:44.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ambil jalan memutar!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bersiaplah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.75,0:09:49.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.66,0:10:06.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuda-kuda yang terlibat situasi ini\Nbenar-benar sial, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.66,0:10:08.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, silakan kabur.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.29,0:10:15.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang benar saja?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.39,0:10:26.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo, pergilah.\NBiar kami yang menahannya!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.82,0:10:29.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Teoritta!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.07,0:10:32.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kesatriaku!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.00,0:10:34.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pinjamkan aku kekuatanmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.17,0:10:35.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita kalahkan mereka!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.67,0:10:40.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa engkau sudah menyadari\Nbetapa pentingnya seorang Dewi?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya. Kau sangat penting!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Komandan, lewat sini!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.94,0:10:47.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rajit!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.40,0:10:50.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa Xylo Forbartz bisa mengalahkan itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita mulai!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.00,0:10:58.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kesatriaku, selesaikanlah dengan cepat!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.23,0:11:21.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.95,0:11:22.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah menolongku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.19,0:11:25.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.80,0:11:28.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah bagian terpenting,\Nyaitu pujiannya belum?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.86,0:11:36.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak menginginkan pujian\Ndari siapa pun selain kesatriaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.71,0:11:41.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo, aku ingin dengar, "Kau hebat,"\Ndari mulutmu langsung.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.28,0:11:49.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sungguh Dewi yang hebat.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.56,0:12:02.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang baru saja terjadi...?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.16,0:12:04.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah paham sekarang, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.29,0:12:07.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama kau berniat menebus seluruh dosamu,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.06,0:12:09.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,maka aku akan berikan pengampunan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.76,0:12:14.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa sebenarnya kalian?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.02,0:12:18.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan dorong-dorong!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.10,0:12:23.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.23,0:12:27.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kota yang telah diwariskan leluhurku...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.30,0:12:31.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak, jangan terlalu jauh dariku!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.95,0:12:34.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.00,0:12:34.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iri.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.95,0:12:36.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.31,0:12:42.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya, aku enggan melakukan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.93,0:12:45.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku diancam oleh orang\Nyang sangat menyeramkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.54,0:12:47.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jujur, aku tak ingin lakukan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.61,0:12:49.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak...!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.46,0:12:51.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku merasa bersalah padamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.04,0:12:54.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kumohon, ikutlah denganku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.10,0:12:57.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku takkan menyakitimu, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keributannya besar sekali, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.56,0:13:19.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya terjadi masalah\Nyang lumayan besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.01,0:13:22.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin Lideo Sodrick telah tewas.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.14,0:13:24.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kondisinya parah sekali, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.00,0:13:30.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku sudah pergi ke lapangan,\Ntapi kliennya malah tewas?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.33,0:13:35.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau tak ada upah, aku tak mau ikut.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pamit.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.56,0:13:43.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita kumpulkan uang dari Guild Petualang,\Nlalu pergi dari kota.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Boojum, bagaimana denganmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.50,0:13:49.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan pergi menolong Lideo Sodrick.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.20,0:13:51.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itulah cara membalas budi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.60,0:13:52.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau serius?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.70,0:13:55.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia telah mengurusku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.60,0:13:58.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, aku tak akan meminta...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm? Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu. Sampai di sini saja, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sungguh disayangkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.46,0:14:12.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada perintah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.00,0:14:15.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku diminta membuang Lideo Sodrick.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.06,0:14:19.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian mengincar uang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.00,0:14:21.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kalian mau menerima pekerjaan baru?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.46,0:14:23.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.35,0:14:25.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Permintaan dari siapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.23,0:14:27.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu tidak sopan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.07,0:14:51.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Boojum, kau...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.13,0:14:53.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami akan bayar upahnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.41,0:14:57.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan begitu,\Nmanusia akan bekerja dengan giat, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama dapat uang,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.36,0:15:06.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,entah itu petualang atau Malapetaka Raja Iblis,\Nmereka semua klien terhormatku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.58,0:15:09.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, apa yang kau incar, Klien Terhormat?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.93,0:15:12.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya, klienmu bukan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.76,0:15:19.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertama-tama, aku diperintahkan menghapus\Nseluruh hubungan kami dengan Lideo Sodrick.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.40,0:15:21.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hapus tanpa jejak, secara harfiah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke. Itu kebolehanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.43,0:15:28.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih atas kerja samamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.76,0:15:31.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shiji Bau, bagaimana denganmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.61,0:15:36.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau orang yang bertugas mendidikku.\NAku berutang budi padamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.60,0:15:39.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku enggan membunuhmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.46,0:15:44.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau memintaku\Nberkhianat dari umat manusia?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.83,0:15:47.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau ada masalah dengan itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.42,0:15:52.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku belajar hal penting dari Lideo Sodrick.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.10,0:15:58.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Manusia adalah makhluk yang mengutamakan\Nkeselamatan diri sendiri dan keluarganya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.80,0:16:05.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apalagi jika itu berhubungan\Ndengan keuntungan pribadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.16,0:16:09.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hal seperti itu lebih penting\Ndari keberlangsungan seluruh ras.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.36,0:16:12.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itulah manusia. Apa aku salah?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.86,0:16:17.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.60,0:16:19.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kawal kami dari segala arah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tebus dosamu dengan\Nbekerja sebagai bawahanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.43,0:16:28.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bekerjalah untuk kebaikan rakyat kita!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.00,0:16:29.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.00,0:16:31.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya, kita berangkat!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.50,0:16:32.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Si-Siap!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.70,0:16:37.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami akan memeriksa lantai dua.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.76,0:16:42.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin saja ada bukti fisik.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.14,0:16:46.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, akui kesalahanmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mintalah maaf atas seluruh kesalahan\Nyang telah engkau lakukan!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.38,0:16:52.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.54,0:16:55.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya orang ini terpesona\Npada sosok sang "Dewi"!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.78,0:16:56.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kelihatannya tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kelihatan, kok!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.23,0:17:01.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, katakan semua yang engkau tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.11,0:17:02.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akui,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.65,0:17:06.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku pernah bermaksud membunuh kalian\Nsebagai pemimpin Guild Petualang.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.82,0:17:09.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku tak tahu apa-apa soal klienku.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.60,0:17:12.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, kedengarannya tidak baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.12,0:17:13.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan langsung percaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.05,0:17:20.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekadar informasi,\Nsituasimu saat ini benar-benar dirugikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.13,0:17:24.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seharusnya, kami menyerahkanmu\Npada pihak Kesatria Suci.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bisa akali supaya itu tak terjadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.99,0:17:30.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, jangan mulai negosiasi\Ntanpa izin dariku!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.43,0:17:33.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, mau pakai ancaman\Nyang lebih sederhana?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.18,0:17:35.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menurutku, dia sudah terbiasa\Nmenghadapi kekerasan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.89,0:17:39.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau menawarkan negosiasi,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.90,0:17:42.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,apa kau akan menerima syarat dariku?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.23,0:17:44.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dengar dulu isinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.03,0:17:48.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin adik perempuan dan laki-lakiku...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin keluargaku selamat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.10,0:17:53.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudmu anak-anak yang ngeri itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.22,0:17:56.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama kau berjanji\Ntakkan mencelakai mereka,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.43,0:17:59.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku akan mempertimbangkan tawaranmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.84,0:18:04.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.81,0:18:07.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo, kau tak punya kuasa untuk itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.70,0:18:10.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, mau cari dan bunuh mereka?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.16,0:18:14.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita siksa anak-anak itu satu\Nper satu di depan matanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak pernah bilang itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.28,0:18:18.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, tutup mulutmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.27,0:18:19.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lideo Sodrick.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katakan semua yang bisa kau katakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.63,0:18:23.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini negosiasi yang sederhana, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.43,0:18:27.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tujuannya adalah membunuh "Dewi".
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.86,0:18:33.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Klien kami adalah kelompok\Nyang mengaku bernama "Faksi Koeksistensi".
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.80,0:18:36.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi-lagi nama faksi itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.83,0:18:39.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepuluh hari yang lalu,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.10,0:18:42.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku pertama kali bertemu\Ndengan pria bertopeng hitam.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.23,0:18:48.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka bilang ini negosiasi,\Ntapi tak memberikan pilihan untukku.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.09,0:18:52.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Patuh, hidup berdampingan, atau mati...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.82,0:18:59.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah itu, aku berkomunikasi\Nmelalui perantara sebanyak tiga kali.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka ada di berbagai tempat.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.79,0:19:06.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau tak ingin mati,\Naku harus tunjukkan kalau aku berguna.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.63,0:19:11.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau terlalu takut mati sampai\Nmengkhianati umat manusia?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.16,0:19:13.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian pasti bisa melawan mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.18,0:19:17.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Faksi Koeksistensi ingin\Nmenyerahkan kekuasaan pada Raja Iblis,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.80,0:19:21.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan mengatur seluruh umat\Nmanusia di bawah rezim itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.00,0:19:25.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Intinya, para budak,\Npengawas budak, dan penguasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka telah mencemari berbagai wilayah,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.45,0:19:31.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,banyak nyawa yang direnggut,\Ndan tanah yang dirusak.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.17,0:19:34.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau dibiarkan saja,\Numat manusia akan kalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.43,0:19:39.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, setidaknya aku harus\Nmasuk ke dalam barisan para pengawas.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.53,0:19:42.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini penting demi keluargaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.56,0:19:45.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak ingin dengar alasanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.91,0:19:47.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katakan informasi yang lebih berguna!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.06,0:19:49.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau tidak, negosiasi kita dibatalkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.90,0:19:53.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pria bertopeng hitam...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.43,0:19:57.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pernah dengar namanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.30,0:20:00.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katakan. Toh pasti pakai nama palsu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.30,0:20:04.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mahaeyzel Zelkoff.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pasti bercanda.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mahaeyzel itu nama tokoh suci.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.56,0:20:12.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ia pemimpin Kuil saat\NPembasmian Raja Iblis yang pertama.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.66,0:20:15.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain itu, Zelkoff...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.06,0:20:17.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau Zelkoff...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.23,0:20:21.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, katakan sekali...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.25,0:20:25.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Raja! Raja!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.33,0:20:27.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.10,0:20:28.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita diserang?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.00,0:20:34.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya demi uang.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.01,0:20:36.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terkuburlah dalam diam.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ba-Bangunannya...!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.60,0:20:43.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita kabur ke luar!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.92,0:20:46.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ini? Ada apa ini?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.27,0:20:48.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada pasukan artileri, dong.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.99,0:20:54.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Xylo, cepatlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.63,0:20:55.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kivia, cepat...!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.99,0:20:56.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.77,0:20:58.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pria itu, dia...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.04,0:21:00.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.68,0:21:01.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.76,0:21:04.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita kabur, kau cari mati, ya?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.56,0:21:13.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada tembakan lain, merunduk!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.34,0:21:20.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini kenapa, sih?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.41,0:21:24.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sinting, ya?\NKenapa lakukan ini di tengah kota?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.03,0:21:26.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial. Andai saja ada Neely di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.53,0:21:29.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, jangan salahkan Neely.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.43,0:21:30.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mau kubunuh, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.63,0:21:31.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak menyalahkan dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.15,0:21:34.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika musuh punya pasukan artileri,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.13,0:21:36.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,maka kita perlu kekuatan Rhyno.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.70,0:21:40.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita perlu menyeretnya\Nkeluar dari sel penjara.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.46,0:21:43.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah? Aku tak terlalu suka Rhyno, tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.65,0:21:46.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kivia, kita kejar Lideo Sodrick.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.96,0:21:49.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ba-Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.80,0:21:51.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.81,0:21:58.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entah pria itu berkata jujur atau tidak...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.29,0:22:00.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus pastikan semuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.93,0:22:09.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.36,0:22:12.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iri?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.62,0:22:13.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaukah itu, Iri?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.32,0:22:15.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.55,0:22:17.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iri!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.76,0:22:19.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.75,0:22:22.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Be-Benar, entah bagaimana.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.38,0:22:26.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Guild kita lenyap, tapi nyawa masih ada.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.04,0:22:29.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di mana anak-anak yang lain?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.00,0:22:33.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain beberapa yang tertangkap\NKesatria Suci, mereka ada di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.76,0:22:35.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.80,0:22:38.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sempat melakukan beberapa negosiasi...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.60,0:22:41.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kalian semua akan baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.10,0:22:42.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Negosiasi?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.70,0:22:48.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak, kau membocorkan apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:48.02,0:22:50.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, aku tak katakan hal-hal yang penting.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:51.23,0:22:52.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:53.72,0:22:55.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iri?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:02.02,0:23:05.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, Kak. Ini untuk berjaga-jaga.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.44,0:23:16.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ka-Kau...? Di mana Iri...?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.49,0:23:18.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sudah mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.27,0:23:20.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku meminjam tubuh dan otaknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.80,0:23:23.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak-anakmu yang lain ada di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.29,0:23:29.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ti-Tidak mungkin...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.03,0:23:31.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keluargaku
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.70,0:23:35.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang begitu berharga...!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.36,0:23:40.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat tinggal,\Npria yang pernah menjadi kakakku.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:55.55,0:23:59.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya kita perlu\Nmempercepat rencananya.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:59.96,0:24:02.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulai persiapan untuk hancurkan kota ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.39,0:24:07.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Basmi seluruh manusia,\Ndan hanguskan seluruh benda fisik.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.16,0:24:10.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terutama "Dewi" Teoritta.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.20,0:24:13.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita harus membunuhnya,\Nberapa pun harga yang harus dibayar.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.10,0:24:16.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau bisa berikan aku sedikit waktu?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:17.37,0:24:20.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin mengubur Lideo Sodrick.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.05,0:24:23.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak perlu lakukan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.12,0:24:26.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau diperintahkan untuk mematuhi perintahku.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.50,0:24:32.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, Lideo Sodrick.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:32.00,0:24:34.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah membelikan aku buku.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:35.10,0:24:37.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan hanya Boojum,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:37.00,0:24:39.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,kami butuh bantuan kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:39.60,0:24:43.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja,\Naku akan berikan upah sesuai janji.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:44.83,0:24:48.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik. Namun, izinkan aku menanyakan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:48.83,0:24:51.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus memanggilmu dengan nama apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:51.90,0:24:53.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Spriggan.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:54.60,0:24:56.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong panggil aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:57.21,0:24:59.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Spriggan.
